00:43:23,601 --> 00:43:25,292
Well, what do you know?

453
00:43:25,362 --> 00:43:27,304
Thanks, Harry.

454
00:43:27,378 --> 00:43:29,320
I saw you fight.

455
00:43:29,394 --> 00:43:32,810
Harry Noble,
the human locomotive.

456
00:43:32,883 --> 00:43:34,955
Come on, Harry,
say something.

457
00:43:35,027 --> 00:43:36,588
Talk to me.

458
00:43:38,100 --> 00:43:41,166
Come on, Frank.
Get on with it.

