00:43:46,453 --> 00:43:49,999
Just watches TV.
Loves the commercials.

463
00:43:52,278 --> 00:43:54,285
It's all we got.

464
00:43:56,023 --> 00:43:58,609
Come on. Take it.

465
00:43:58,679 --> 00:44:01,908
It's OK.
We're neighbors.

