00:44:34,077 --> 00:44:37,078
He had a hell of a right.
You should've seen him.

469
00:44:57,249 --> 00:45:01,111
Look out. Flying pot.

470
00:45:01,186 --> 00:45:03,740
Ghost in the garbage!

471
