00:46:32,434 --> 00:46:34,409
Are you superstitious?

488
00:46:34,481 --> 00:46:36,554
I'm getting there.

489
00:46:36,626 --> 00:46:37,936
Well...

490
00:46:39,955 --> 00:46:41,962
I'm not superstitious...

491
00:46:42,995 --> 00:46:45,811
but I was thinking
about these things

492
00:46:45,876 --> 00:46:47,250
and why they came.

493
00:46:47,316 --> 00:46:48,210
Uh-huh.

494
00:46:48,276 --> 00:46:50,349
And, uh...

495
00:46:51,668 --> 00:46:53,524
This will really
sound silly,

496
00:46:53,589 --> 00:46:56,721
but it's like they were
watching or listening.

