526
00:48:21,093 --> 00:48:22,523
What?

527
00:48:22,597 --> 00:48:25,347
Maybe they're here,
those things,

528
00:48:25,415 --> 00:48:27,487
because of you.

529
00:48:39,176 --> 00:48:40,551
Give me back
my camera, man.

530
00:48:40,617 --> 00:48:42,472
Unexplained phenomena, man.

